01:02:57.130 --> 01:03:00.270
That the chronicles
and the biographies

01:03:00.270 --> 01:03:05.770
and so forth we have are you
know the earliest manuscripts

01:03:05.770 --> 01:03:10.760
that we can date, and the dates of
the authors are you know, from 150,

01:03:10.760 --> 01:03:14.160
200, 300 years after
the time of the prophet.

01:03:14.160 --> 01:03:17.640
So that makes a person
nervous as a historian.

01:03:17.640 --> 01:03:21.450
Because you know, I can't remember
what I had for dinner last week.

01:03:21.450 --> 01:03:26.110 position:56%
And depending on people for a memory

01:03:26.110 --> 01:03:29.180
of 300 years before
