01:03:37.260 --> 01:03:39.390
than one hand and over time.

01:03:39.390 --> 01:03:41.780
And for any of the
more pious Muslims

01:03:41.780 --> 01:03:43.260
in the audience, I apologize.

01:03:43.260 --> 01:03:47.650 position:56%
