have been siding with Iran.

01:07:40.030 --> 01:07:43.570
And Muhammad was talking up
the Holy Land and the prophets

01:07:43.570 --> 01:07:46.100
of Jerusalem and Jesus and Moses.

01:07:46.100 --> 01:07:49.230
And the pagans might well have
been saying to him, "Well,

01:07:49.230 --> 01:07:51.210
your Jerusalem is gone, isn't it?

01:07:51.210 --> 01:07:54.850
It's in the hands of the
