01:07:54.850 --> 01:07:57.740
And so I think maybe
having a vision of it

01:07:57.740 --> 01:08:02.940
in which Jerusalem inspires
the prophet is a way

01:08:02.940 --> 01:08:05.870
of spiritually pushing
back against that line.

