01:13:40.990 --> 01:13:45.480
And I don't know how you
reconcile the things that they do

01:13:45.480 --> 01:13:47.030
with the text of the Qur'an.

01:13:47.030 --> 01:13:51.700
You're only supposed
to fight combatants.

01:13:51.700 --> 01:13:53.880
Well, they don't just
