01:13:53.880 --> 01:13:57.790
They kidnap ordinary innocent
people and behead them.

01:13:57.790 --> 01:14:00.530
That's not Qur'anic.

01:14:00.530 --> 01:14:07.270
So to the extent that I'm
comfortable with putting my finger

01:14:07.270 --> 01:14:10.160
on some normative elements
of the Qur'an,

01:14:10.160 --> 01:14:12.780 position:56%
